The '''Faith of the Seven''' is the main [[religion]] of the [[Seven Kingdoms]]. It is little-practiced beyond its borders. The Faith of the Seven is dominant in the south of [[Westeros]]. The only regions where it is not the majority religion areÂ [[the North]], where worship of the [[Old Gods of the Forest]] remains strong, and on the [[Iron Islands]], where the local religion of the [[Drowned God]] is most widespread. There are many exceptions in all three areas, however.&lt;ref name=&quot;VG Gods Old and New&quot;&gt;[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-of-thrones/season2/#!/guide/appendix/gods-old-and-new/ HBO viewers guide, season 2 appendix, Gods Old and New entry]&lt;/ref&gt;
